snippet.title: Amber Marshall | Heartland season 14
snippet.description:
Actor @Amber Marshall sat down to talk with us from her home about the 14th season of @Heartland on CBC. The new season was safely filmed during the pandemic, and required some changes from the script, once they started shooting. Marshall also chatted about one of the main storylines for Amy this season.

#Heartland #ILoveHeartland
